description: The iShares iBonds 2027 Term High Yield and Income ETF seeks to track the investment results of an index composed of U.S. dollar denominated, high yield and other income generating corporate bonds maturing in 2027. This Fund is covered by U.S. Patent Nos. 8,438,100 and 8,655,770.
name: iShares iBonds 2027 Term High Yield and Income ETF
